- CS-001 (2026-04-21): shared-model merge conflict on `src/models/task.ts`. Resolved by installing `@dna-cross-checker`. Pattern: methodology gap → subagent answer.
- CS-002 (2026-04-23): `[D]` partial delivery. 005 shipped server-side, 006 committed as sibling for UI. Resolved at 006 merge. Pattern: Article 5 scope split done correctly.
